info.author: Curro Jerez and Pablo Martin
info.description:
This package allows creation of node custom node editors, featuring unlimited
zoom and nesting, as well as a flexible backend system, to allow using it with
different widget frameworks.
info.name: pynoded
info.summary: Package to create node editors using cairo as backend
info.html_description: This package allows creation of node custom node editors, featuring unlimited zoom and nesting, as well as a flexible backend system, to allow using it with different widget frameworks.
